Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.61,0:02:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 妙傳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺塞拉好像變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是對父親的事釋懷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看來是和納比在一起變得快樂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭就表示喜歡上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最糟糕的是沒有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.53,0:02:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在說遙和詹姆士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經也年輕過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.29,0:02:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就說一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道我是生活在穆尼斯的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前 因為幼稚園的遠足
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到了明暗邊界線的附近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:02:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是穆尼斯和月亮背面的邊界名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在月亮上 跨越邊界到背面是重罪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要終身監禁的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那一天 我回過神來已經迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時很害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了找大家一直跑啊 跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺中已經到了禁止進入的月球背面了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的腳印 巨人先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.05,0:03:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起來那時我也真是單純呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.97,0:03:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穆尼斯上有巨人一直是個祕密呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也因此被擊落呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真做了啊 不過算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在月亮背面看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是和納比同一種族的巨人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我要是大人的話估計就被抓走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那時年幼所以沒被重視
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不管和誰說 都不會相信我看到巨人的腳印了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時不甘心的一直掉眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想著巨人腳印的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回過神來已經成為鞋業設計師了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那時候 我遇到了詹姆士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是第一個笑著聽我講述巨人腳印的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我們交往的契機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 我有說什麼奇怪的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.65,0:04:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙小姐現在還喜歡著詹姆士先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說傻話了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹 快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛翔吧 子彈號
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊 美雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡壞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是腳部的驅動系統
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能修好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 故障本身是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.73,0:05:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算修好下次別的地方又會出問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單單簡單的修理是不夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的駕駛技術已經開始超越它的極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性感B ZEPHYR 還有子彈號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每台都有不同程度的損壞 情況都差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是BF的動力爐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃料是阿魯迪紐姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其運轉功率不知道為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近在一點點的上升
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 動力上去的不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法駕馭的動力爐就像著火的引線
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 更加危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:06:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能置不知道什麼時候會爆炸的東西於不顧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然很聰明呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.46,0:06:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和丹不同哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具體的對策呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能跟上大家的操作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要進行徹底的強化改造
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠這裡的設備是沒法工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止是這些吧 美雪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強化改造還要一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還需要阿魯迪紐姆動力系統的特殊數據
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 美雪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零號地區
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BF的聖地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父親死去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱會的準備進行的很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫日食什麼的演唱的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.53,0:07:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭真的話再次說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會像以前一樣向陛下您傾訴的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以閃電的力量 大地之神的名義
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拜託了 楊．哈里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風在哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今無法訴說的悲傷的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就閒置了很多年來說還不算壞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統也很正常呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求連接 鮎川武
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文件ID M1152
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於控制臨界點的阿魯迪紐姆的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及BF動力系統的應用研究
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始連接
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親留下的研究數據
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們 演唱會的事去問新的經紀人吧 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱會的事瞞著露玖就決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定她會反對這次演唱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 皮歐蕾特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露玖一定會支持你們的決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.73,0:08:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個演唱會背負著世界的未來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.51,0:08:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是為了新的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新看後發現…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種磨損方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是來回轉動卻沒有磨痕 真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:08:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能看出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊 老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道 去問美雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什麼啊 美雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人的話不知道要花多少天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想快點Basqua啊 而且還要快點去月亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真囉嗦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就去睡個午覺 做做你那個偶像的夢去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 誰會那種…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹先生 臉通紅的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 這次讓我隨意發揮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 拜什麼託啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之交給你了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫我丹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.43,0:09:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 美雪 有什麼需要幫忙的就說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好餓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.81,0:09:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍忍吧 美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:09:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就會有好事發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛茲．波雅特 貝爾．林頓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.55,0:10:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 阿蘿拉公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪小姐 還沒吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在那好了 我等會吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然知道她很拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這也太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然說想一個人工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還不吃飯 好像也沒怎麼睡過的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.09,0:10:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去身體會垮掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能讓她按照自己的方式去做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:11:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪作為工程師現在正在向更高的領域邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.31,0:11:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了回應你們進步的操作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她覺得自己也要精進才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再這樣下去會倒下的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘭他們很擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吃過了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是我想快點把這些孩子修好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親留下的數據我希望能幫上大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前在羅納迪克進行阿魯迪紐姆的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅動現在BF的就是當時開發的系統
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我兒子武想要將其再次進化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.93,0:11:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進化？ 是POWER UP嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:12:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 武想把傳說中的巨人以機器的方式再現
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有一次 技術超越了人的掌控發生了失控
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下了巨大的爪痕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是好說 大家都明白新的技術可能會招致新的事故
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了追求真理 這樣的記憶是不可避免的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類難道是如此愚蠢的生物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:40.00,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『主翻』willyer『校正』willyer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪小姐為什麼和已故的父親走上同一條路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像有點能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是想通過工作來感受到父親吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:12:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺為了讓人們的生活更方便而開發了BF
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他教導我BF是讓人們獲得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這個目的應該做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考並付諸於行動的就是技術員了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢 丹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道可可因為BF不能走路之後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和爺爺其實都非常傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著要是沒有BF就不會發生這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科技和酒一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有節制不停的喝的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲早是會滅亡人類的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊 學你爺爺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 追求技術本身成為了目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂這些複雜的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我已經不恨BF了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:14:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有BF的話 也不會有現在的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.87,0:14:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Basquash也就沒有開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都笑了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有了BF
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.39,0:14:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感謝爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過撕爛我的嘴也不會說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得吃飯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 斯帕奇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯嗎 真想吃好吃的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝爾那份留著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他睡著了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風啊 雲啊 大地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:15:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的靈魂的平靜歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人在練習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算什麼練習 反正也很閒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我陪你練也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要誤會 我也只是很閒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我不是想和你Basquash才這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好奇怪的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有BF要怎麼練習呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是想待在一起直說不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克羅莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用這麼笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:15:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好 塞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會笑了 不要再生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 不能輸給美雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁這個機會 要完成超級鞋底樣式和
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全旋轉模式繪圖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好忙 好忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉色不太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爺 我這樣下去好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.27,0:16:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很清楚自己要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我到底要做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能一直這樣下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小歇一會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 你來看下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡 父親的圖紙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有幾個地方空著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 確實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且控制能量直接連接在核心部份
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可真有那小子的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是兒子的想法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 什麼 告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說要一個人完成的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 這也是為了可愛的孫女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.71,0:17:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你一點提示吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖紙是為了給人看的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也有不讓自己遺忘的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武沒有在圖紙上畫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說根本不用擔心會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 是初期係數 還有物理點數吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速度？ 圓周率？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 父親是技術員
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是能量轉換率 還是摩擦係數？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 空著的地方有3個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是三形矩陣不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不變的東西 不變的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不變的強度 不變的規定值
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 衝阿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能成功著陸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 這是我的得意之作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 一點都沒變阿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內在啦 內在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從頭到腳的內部都徹底換過了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抱怨先坐上去再說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:19:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼內在變化 和以前一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.76,0:19:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 發覺變化了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有多餘的動作了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且很圓滑 一點都不生硬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人一目了然的進化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹的好 你已經能獨當一面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.51,0:19:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武一定也會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害呢 這樣的BF我從沒見過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整體感完全不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像連指尖都連有神經一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太出色了 美雪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:20:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然很厲害啊 美雪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她累壞了 讓她睡會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.82,0:20:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總這麼勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 這樣就能上月球了 等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是回憶 我的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是露玖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識這些人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西朵隆 皮歐蕾特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我重要的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.29,0:20:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露玖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.19,0:20:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.41,0:21:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 露玖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.38,0:21:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是露玖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重生後的感覺怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺？ 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.12,0:21:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 一定是做了什麼悲傷的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向楊．哈里斯總經理報告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他露玖的準備已經完成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲傷的夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.37,0:21:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 我被爺爺稱讚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.43,0:21:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我能獨當一面了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能看見吧 父親的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天它們也一定能登上月球
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.63,0:22:09.20,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}夜空高懸 清風吹拂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.63,0:22:09.20,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}空は高く風は流れて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.29,0:22:12.51,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}月的鼓動化解在黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.29,0:22:12.51,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}月の波動 闇に融けてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:16.15,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}所以現在只需要向前前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:16.15,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}だから 今は前だけを向き
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.19,0:22:19.35,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Believe Your Love 相信這條路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.19,0:22:19.35,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Believe Your Love この道を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.45,0:22:22.96,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}大海深涵 波濤湧動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.45,0:22:22.96,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}海は深く 波は寄せてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:26.18,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}將你的心靈打動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:26.18,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}きみの心ごわめいていく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.25,0:22:29.76,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}所以現在只需抬頭看天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.25,0:22:29.76,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}だから 今は上だけを見て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.86,0:22:33.13,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Believe Your Love 相信這心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.86,0:22:33.13,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Believe Your Love この气持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.05,0:22:40.30,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}將那嘆息的星座指向
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.05,0:22:40.30,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}嘆きの星座の調べを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.39,0:22:43.52,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}銘刻在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.39,0:22:43.52,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}胸に刻み
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:48.09,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}然後出發前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:48.09,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}そして走り出す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.42,0:22:51.86,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}我們總是抱著煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.42,0:22:51.86,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}僕らはいつも悩みながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.91,0:22:55.35,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}尋找那瞬間的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.91,0:22:55.35,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}刹那の希望探している
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.41,0:22:58.57,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}那黑白交織的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.41,0:22:58.57,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}白と黑とが交わるとき
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.97,0:23:02.15,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}一定一定 在那無盡的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.97,0:23:02.15,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}きっと きっと 果てなく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:05.64,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}光的盡頭 會有我們的路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:05.64,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}光の先に 見える道を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.68,0:23:08.95,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}我夢見我們倆走在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.68,0:23:08.95,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}二人で歩く夢を見たよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:12.66,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}可愛的 那是我幾近忘卻的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:12.66,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}愛しさ それは忘れていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:16.05,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}對你的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:16.05,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}きみへの約束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.19,0:23:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日食在這次蔚藍王國演唱會後將要解散
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.51,0:23:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日食要…我的日食…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.46,0:23:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 要為我們加油到最後哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.31,0:23:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解散？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.96,0:23:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露玖
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.75,0:25:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,


